    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/8d42fefbec8f8711fc14c130d7c03997.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内容摘要</h2>Puzzle Dazzle》是一款独特、令人上瘾、令人叹为观止的经典方块益智游戏。充满活力的音乐与华丽的美术同步进行，创造出令人着迷的紧张刺激的整体体验。在策略性地匹配方块和完成目标的同时，尽情享受悦耳的音乐、平静的旋律、灵动的背景和壮观的特效。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.poster.avif?t=1744899219\" width=720 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.webm?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/6d7aaec7e6c36f8d7f66714ab45ebc47.mp4?t=1744899219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >街机模式： 进入视觉盛宴！</h2>我们精心设计了 50 个独特的关卡，这些关卡都设置在超现实的景观中。每个关卡都是一场视觉盛宴，图形和游戏性完美融合，使街机模式成为一场真正的感官盛宴！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存模式： 跻身排行榜前列！</h2>与时间赛跑，努力超越全球竞争对手，确保自己在排行榜上名列前茅。在此模式中，耐力与策略并存，为您带来肾上腺素飙升的体验，让您流连忘返。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧院模式： 沉浸在绚丽的视觉效果中！</h2>沉浸在剧院模式的独特体验中，《谜题炫斗》将游戏超越为视觉奇观。享受音乐与图形的和谐同步，让剧院模式成为身临其境的体验。让自己沉醉在剧院模式的视觉交响乐中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1588790/extras/fd86fadda96000cab8e5e8cbc663f1f1.poster.avif?t=1744899